    "It outperforms all the systems presented in the literature.",
    "The best results were obtained by CUTE (macro-F1: 67.3, micro-F1: 67.7) [85] 5 -(1) MVET dataset [192] The best-obtained F1-score (0.636) was achieved using three languages, English, German and Spanish where English is relatively more important (SIRE) tool.",
